<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.1">
<l>emmā vīṭṭu tiṟamuñ ceppaniṉ</l>
<l>cemmā pāta paṟput talaicērt tollai</l>
<l>kaimmā tuṉpaṅ kaṭinta pirāṉē</l>
<l>yammā vaṭiyēṉ vēṇṭuva tītē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We won’t talk about our great liberation.</l>
<l>Consent  to [our] joining [our] head to your great red feet lotuses,</l>
<l>o lord who chased away the distress of the hand-animal (~ elephant).</l>
<l>O father, I, [your] servant, need this.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
